   - distinguish 2 'export' variants: EXPORT PROC|CONST|ENUM|OBJECT etc (keyword.control) vs. OPT EXPORT (keyword)
   - distinguish 3 'of' variants: ARRAY OF vs. PROC lala() OF lulu vs. OBJECT lala OF lulu
   - distinguish 2 'is' variants: ENDPROC IS vs. LIBRARY IS
   - distinguish 2 'to' variants: PTR TO vs. FOR TO STEP
